{"tid":1567422,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解最近咁多吹捧藍絲嘅post？","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:41:01.000Z","uid":108502,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ceddd35ac70bd6b41320af4b162e906f989bab07","tid":1567422,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲post淨係不斷話藍絲好勁呀進化呀<br />\n你哋咪撚再笑佢哋呀，再笑就輸架啦<br />\n咁建議呢？係冇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為根本唔會有解決辦法，淨係喺度散播恐慌<br />\n<br />\n乜藍絲有組織力係第一日嘅事？<br />\n你睇下平時佢哋打人、拆文宣、撐警集會就知<br />\n佢哋不嬲都做緊類似嘅嘢<br />\n但佢哋做唔到任何有實際影響嘅行動<br />\n至於咩外媒洗版全部template嚟，你估啲鬼佬睇唔出係五毛／propaganda？<br />\n價值觀完全相反鬼佬邊有可能認同<br />\n<br />\n佢哋唯一一樣有能力影響嘅就係我哋士氣<br />\n所以唔將佢哋當一回事笑鳩佢哋係最佳嘅解決辦法<br />\n將時間同行動力浪費喺群眾鬥群眾上面<br />\n得益嘅係邊個相信唔使我多講"},{"pid":"36238eaf9d6e6785160ac99c4d662df5f7cadf33","tid":1567422,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e237d895bb9336d8941472733c322b208321910","tid":1567422,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:28:14.000Z","msg":"香港人靜係識退<br />\n比藍絲打都以和為貴，好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f6c61580d7745934bd8ef78fc0ffba5340fe44","tid":1567422,"uid":108502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e237d895bb9336d8941472733c322b208321910","tid":1567422,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:28:14.000Z","msg":"香港人靜係識退<br />\n比藍絲打都以